      "id": "PopularPost238676",
      "post_content": "A little underrated by some. As others have pointed, it's costed perfectly for a 3/3 and isn't locked into a color. So at a minimum, you are getting (what should be at least) the standard. Team that with having a bomb in your hand in case you are dealing with discard, and you have a solid card.  \n  \nBest used in ANY sideboard in case you have to deal with fear, intimidate, or discard.  \n  \nI'll give it a 3.5/5",
